,01b746_02c16a4e5b2043418a27f52ca14c7c5d~mv2.jpg;01b746_dd7208aa321e40889bb8a7c4b22c31f7~mv2.jpg;01b746_103b0990b84f4900b464e65cd65bdd8a~mv2.jpg;01b746_aba92f9cd63847369d253e6c4821b3b8~mv2.jpg;01b746_331fbd3dba104e5fa17013d8be845b1a~mv2.jpg;01b746_08cb17205e7f42de9dc6c0bfa177d8e1~mv2.jpg;01b746_367b92528e8b44dabfd02e38416f735b~mv2.jpg,,,,31.0,,true,PERCENT,0.0,InStock,0.0,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,About The Chronicle Photo Journal,"

After countless conversations with travelers, students, parents, artists, and more, we crafted The Chronicle - a photo journal designed to bring a modern twist to a classic photo album. Beautiful, functional, and simple, it is the perfect home for your memories.
The Chronicle Photo Journal comes with a pack of 10 journal cards. You can purchase extra journal cards here.

To our UK customers:  The UK has placed a VAT of 20% on goods valued up to $180 USD, effective Jan 1, 2021. As we are still navigating this new rule, we are unable to fulfill orders to the UK for the time being. Thanks for your patience, and we'll keep you updated!

Enhance your photo journal with additional journal cards! These 4""x6"" cards are much sturdier and more durable than your average flashcards, perfect for your notes and creations.
